com.bobman159.rundml.core.sql

Class AbstractSQLClauseHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bobman159.rundml.core.sql.AbstractSQLClauseHandler

  • public abstract class AbstractSQLClauseHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract handler to create a text SQL statement clause. Uses Chain of Responsibility pattern, the request is handled by only one of the handlers in the chain.
